title: [Eilithyia's General Store]
description: Plain wooden walls rise from an unfinished wooden floor.  Just above an elegantly woven reed mat hangs a trio-bladed mounted vellum fan, and a swirl-painted white stucco ceiling completes the picture.  A damaged packing crate and a plain wooden table stand side by side in the middle of the room.

Refined oak-paneled walls rise from a white limestone floor.  Just above an elegantly woven reed mat hangs a trio-bladed mounted vellum fan, and a swirl-painted white stucco ceiling completes the picture.  A cedar and oak footlocker and a plain wooden table stand side by side in the middle of the room.
